dcterms:description: A collection of user behaviors from Taobao’s recommender system. The dataset contains four types of user behaviors, including click, purchase, adding to cart, and adding to wishlist. The click behaviors are sorted according to time to construct the behavior sequence.
dcterms:title: Taobao Dataset

dcterms:description: Collected from the authors' e-commerce system, this dataset consists of impression logs data of search results page, including user’s historical click sequence and search query sequence with timestamps.
dcterms:title: Industrial Dataset
